  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Our classroom fish, Bubbles, was found dead in his little tank this morning, and honestly, the whole class went quiet for a full minute.",
      "zh": "我們教室的魚 Bubbles 今天早上被發現死在牠的小魚缸裡，老實說，全班安靜了整整一分鐘。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bubbles had been our class pet since the first week of school, so his sudden death felt bigger than a fish probably should.",
      "zh": "Bubbles 從開學第一週就是我們班的寵物，所以牠突然的死亡感覺比一條魚應該有的份量還重。"
